  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went, and there were about three or four children-- my cousins-- all my cousins, myself and my cousin [GERMAN], who is slightly older, who was then 12, and another cousin, Damka, who was 16, and Jurek, a cousin who was maybe 18 or 19, and an uncle who was maybe just over 20-- my youngest uncle-- 20, 21.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got into this flat, and my mother and my aunt went somewhere else, probably to this clinic, so we were left, those four children-- some children and some adolescents, these young men, five of us, left in this flat.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, without any warning, we had screams and shouting and whistles outside and a horrendous noise.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we ran to the window, looking onto [NON-ENGLISH], and we saw already-- it all was happening in seconds practically.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a good practice, and they were doing it very quickly so this street was already all closed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were Ukrainians and police everyone, and they were coming to the-- to the yards-- courtyards-- and shouting for everybody to come immediately down, and immediately the people started going down.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were-- I remember that we were running like rabbits from one window to another and from one window to the window in the back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were opinions among us were divided whether were we all really panic stricken and we really were in a state of shock anyway and whether to go down or not to go down.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And only this one cousin of mine, Anya, who was then 12-- she was just 12-- and she decided not to go down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she went and hid in a hiding place on some shelf in some cupboard in a dark corner, so to say it was a big flat.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
